description: Austrians are urged not to meet people from outside their households as hospitals feel the pressure.
title: Coronavirus: Austria locks down as new wave grips Europe
title_page: Coronavirus: Austria locks down as new wave grips Europe - BBC News
maintext: That figure was nine times higher than at the peak of the initial wave earlier this year. The country has recorded more than 191,000 cases since the start of the pandemic, and 1,661 Covid-related deaths.
